text: "Quantico" and "Baywatch" star Priyanka Chopra is taking over the world. Just a short time after stunning on the Met Gala carpet, Priyanka Chopra invites Vogue in and answers 73 unexpected questions. Priyanka tells us what her favorite thing about America is, her crush on Tupac, and that time she ate worms!
title: Priyanka Chopra Sings Taylor Swift, Tries a Boston Accent, and Beats Up a Clown
